{
  "text": "Since gauge-mediation typically features a light, sub-GeV gravitino, proton decay to K + e G through the diagram in Fig. 11 may be kinematically allowed. The rate for this process is [CITATION_1] and the lifetime for this channel must be longer than 2.3 \u21e5 10 33 yrs., so the gravitino mass bound is",
